<div class="city-card">
  <div class="eyebrow">Space Type</div>
  <h1>{{ spaceType.pluralLabel }} in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}</h1>
  <p class="lead">
  {{ spaceType.label }} space in {{ city.city }} can vary widely depending on location, building type, and how the space is used. 
  Some options are publicly listed, while others are available through local networks or change frequently. 
  The best way to approach your search is to define your requirements early and compare a small set of realistic options across different areas of the market.
  </p>

  <div class="pill-nav-card">
    {% include "partials/space-type/pill-nav.njk" %}
  </div>
</div>